ratd - Daemon for Route Reconstruction

This program is an user-space daemon. It performs a route reconstruction procedure after an attack. At the end of the process, the real packet source and the attack route are informed to the user. For more information, please visit: http://www.gta.ufrj.br/rat/rat_system.html

See INSTALL for building instructions, COPYING for
the license.

After installing, you have to configure your system. See "user-manual.pdf" for details.

